p.k: Hawkodile is the toughest action hero in the land, until his old rival shows up to take vengeance on him. / When Master Frown’s head gets stuck on Unikitty’s butt, she vows to help him get his own body back, but sharing a body with Master Frown can get pretty complicated! / When a giant monster attacks, the gang fights back with Dr. Fox’s new secret weapon: a mega robot! But after the threat is contained, Unikitty doesn’t want to stop using the robot. / Master Frown causes Unikitty to have an angry outburst that gets a little too destructive…
